reviews.review_text: Argh!!! The best part of the show (Jam after drums) is tragically cut short just as it really starts to heat up! Reminds me of the tragic cut in the similar Jam—also out of drums—on 4/24/70. Unlike that one, there may be small hope for a patch here…pretty please?
